<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Follower</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #8B5CF6;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background-color: #8B5CF6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .follower-box {
            background-color: #F5F3FF;
            border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ You Have a New Follower!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

        <p>Great news! <strong>{{followerName}}</strong> started following you on TCG Marketplace.</p>

        <div class="follower-box">
            <p><strong>{{followerName}}</strong> is now following your profile and will see your latest products and activities in their feed.</p>
        </div>

        {{#if actionUrl}}
        <center>
            <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="button">View Profile</a>
        </center>
        {{/if}}

        <p>Keep building your community by engaging with your followers and listing great products!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>You're receiving this email because you've enabled follower notifications.</p>
            <p><a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="color: #8B5CF6;">Manage your notification preferences</a></p>
            <p>&copy; {{year}} TCG Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
